snippet: Mayor Eric Garcetti seems to embody a host of ethnic, ideological and cultural strains that are transforming the city, but unlike his predecessor, he strives to avoid the spotlight.
abstract: Election of Los Angeles Mayor Eric Garcetti has brought attention to city's shifting political and cultural geography; Garcetti seems to embody host of ethnic, ideological and cultural strains that are transforming LA, but unlike his predecessor, he strives to avoid spotlight.
lead_paragraph: Mayor Eric Garcetti seems to embody a host of ethnic, ideological and cultural strains that are transforming the city, but unlike his predecessor, he strives to avoid the spotlight.

headline.main: Garcetti, New Los Angeles Mayor, Reflects Changing City
headline.print_headline: A Mayor From the Other Side of Town
